-- Russia's Sberbank <SBER.MM> appoints European banks to arrange eurobond issue - RIA
-- By Alexander Winning
-- Wed Jun 11, 2014 03:40AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, June 11 (Reuters) - Russia's top lender Sberbank <SBER.MM> has appointed several European investment banks to arrange a eurobond issue denominated in euros, RIA news agency reported on Wednesday, citing a source close to the bank.

